  "text": "While distinct network-level electrical phenotype have been reported for neurons coupled to conductive thin-films of carbon nanotubes [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , and attributed to specific electrical properties of the substrate [CITATION_3] , GO and rGO seem to largely leave neuronal network formation ex vivo unaltered.",
